"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/909282","Women and Equalities","false","2018-06-08","<p>GEO does work with consultants hired under contract working on e.g. the gender pay gap portal, but these people would be procured for such activity via the government procurement service, and are not GEO employees.</p>","Louth and Horncastle","Victoria Atkins",,"2018-06-08T11:24:15.327Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/909282/answer","Biography information for Victoria Atkins","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/909282/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/909282/answer",,,,,"31","Women and Equalities","Women and Equalities","2018-05-22","Government Equalities Office: Procurement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for Women and Equalities, how many contractors her Department employs who have worked for her Department for (a) up to one year, (b) over one and up to five years, (c) over five years and up to ten years and (d) over 10 years.","false","Biography information for Philip Davies","Shipley","Philip Davies","146795"
