"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/909289","Department for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","false","2018-06-04","<p>There are no contractors currently employed by the Department for Digital, Culture, Media &amp; Sport paid more than £1000 a day.</p>","Stourbridge","Margot James",,"2018-06-04T15:35:22.633Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/909289/answer","Biography information for Margot James","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/909289/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/909289/answer",,,,,"10","Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","2018-05-22","Department for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport: Procurement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport, how many contractors currently employed by his Department are paid £1,000 or more per day.","false","Biography information for Philip Davies","Shipley","Philip Davies","146802"
